"created_at": "2022-03-15T10:57:47Z", "updated_at": "2022-03-15T10:57:47Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "如果安装了脚本标签，则除了`src/index.html`，它将自动删除该行为。\r\n\r\n参考：[Angular/Angular＃4903]（https://github.com/angular/angular/angular/issues/4903）\r\n\r\n因此，例如，当安装[Twitter Publish]（https://publish.twitter.com/#）可以获得一个按钮时，存在一个问题，例如Tweet按钮的CSS不会达到。\r\n\r\n＃＃＃ 解决方案\r\n\r\n``TS\r\n导入{component，afterviewInit}来自'@angular/core';\r\n\r\n@零件 （{\r\n  选择器：'app-tweet-btn'，\r\n  模板：`<\r\n    id =“ btn”\r\n    href =“ https://twitter.com/share?ref_src = twsrc5etfw”\r\n    class =“ twitter-share-button”\r\n    数据展示计算=“ false”\r\n    >推文</a\r\n  >`，，\r\n}）\r\n导出类TweetBtnComponent实现AfterViewInit {\r\n  ngafterviewinit（）：void {\r\n    const script = document.createelement（'script'）;\r\n    script.Async = true;\r\n    script.src ='https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js';\r\n    cons btn = document.getElementById（'btn'）！;\r\n    btn.insertadjacentelement（'perthend'，脚本）;\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\n````````\r\n\r\n初始化视图后，生成脚本标签，并在指定标签后面安装了脚本标签。\r\n\r\n当我在此页面标题的底部安装Tweet按钮时，我有点丢失，所以请留下一张便条。", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/17/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/17/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}